edu.kit.cm.kitcampusguide.standardtypes
Class POIQuery

java.lang.Object
  edu.kit.cm.kitcampusguide.standardtypes.POIQuery

public class POIQuery
extends Object

Represents a query for a POI request. Stores the MapSection, a collection of the maps and a collection of the categories that will be filtered by.

Author:
